    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Machines or attachments for a tractor or grader having a long tooth or series of teeth that can be lowered to tear up surface soil or pavement.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
